          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
            This marketing website does not process, store, or transmit Protected Health Information (PHI). Our software products (when launched) will comply with HIPAA requirements and Business Associate Agreements (BAA) will be executed with all clients.
